Operation.Documentation_plain:
Handles the pick up selected order button click event.Retrieves the selected order from the UI and checks if it is ready.If the order is not selected or not ready, displays an error message.If the order is ready, calls the pickUpOrder method of the CoolSuppliesFeatureSet12Controller.If the order is successfully picked up, refreshes the UI.
@author Jiaduo Xing
@since 1.0

